high_descs: Turn right to face toward the sink.
Pick up the knife from the back of the left side of the sink.
Turn around to your left and go to the countertop to the right of the stove.
Slice the potato at the back of the countertop.
Move back slightly from the counter.
Put the knife down on the counter, just behind the fork.
Reach to the back of the counter.
Grab the nearest piece of the sliced potato.
Turn left, go to the end of the counter beyond the stove, then go left to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Put the piece of potato in the fridge, on the shelf above the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of potato into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the left, covered portion of the back of the sink, behind the black cup.
Turn to your left and go towards the window, making a left at the window, then go to the small counter to the right of the stove.
Cut the potato on the back of the counter, behind the spoon, into slices.
Step back from the counter, holding the knife.
Place the knife on the counter, behind the fork.
Step back up to the counter.
Pick up the front potato slice that is on the counter.
Turn to your left and walk past the kitchen island, then turn left after the kitchen and go to the microwave ahead of you.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, heat it, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn to your right, and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice in the refrigerator, on the shelf above the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Start walking across the room to the window, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn left and walk up to the window, then turn left again and walk over to the counter.
Use the butter knife to slice up the potato on the counter.
Look down at the front edge of the counter.
Put the butter knife onto the counter to the left of the fork.
Look up at the sliced potato on the counter.
Pick up the end piece of the sliced potato.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the piece of sliced potato inside, close the door and heat up the potato slice for a couple seconds, then open the door, take the potato slice out and close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the heated potato slice into the fridge on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato slice in the fridge.

anns.task_desc: place a microwave potato slice inside of the fridge
